ygData.messageBody:
Depends on your server. On E'ci I have found that Najena nearly always has
a couple of groups working the front areas and that either Najena or
Bonecracker are camped. Drelzna has been camped every time I've been there
(at east a dozen times).

Kit

-----Original Message-----
From: Pinen [mailto:ubersorcerer@...]
Sent: Friday, March 31, 2000 10:04 AM
To: eqbards@onelist.com
Subject: [eqbards] NAJENA ADVICE PLEASE


As a casual player I'm having a hard time getting out of 23rd level is this
the place for me I'm currently in Sol A but keep dieing...I can solo in SK
and Lake rathe with little or no problem but exp is sloooooooooooow and
finding an open spot in LR is hard.
Pinen
23 bard
